sequenceDiagram

    participant u as Client (Web/App)
    participant s as Server (FastAPI)
    participant asr as Speech-to-Text (Qwen ASR)
    participant vad as VAD Engine (Silero + Smart Turn)
    participant llm as LLM (Azure OpenAI, planned)
    participant tts as TTS (Fish Speech, planned)

    u->>+s: 建立 WebSocket 連線 /ws
    s-->>-u: response.session (session_id)

    par Audio Streaming
        loop 前端持續送音訊
            u->>s: audio chunk (PCM bytes, 24kHz, 16-bit, mono)
            s->>s: 重採樣為 16kHz 並累積 buffer
            s->>asr: input_audio_buffer.append
            asr-->>s: transcription.delta
            s-->>u: response.asr_text (status=partial)
        end
    and VAD Detection
        loop 偵測語音停頓
            s->>vad: record_and_predict(chunk)
            vad-->>s: endpoint detected? (true/false)
            alt 偵測到停頓
                s->>asr: input_audio_buffer.commit
                asr-->>s: transcription.done / response.done
                s-->>u: response.asr_text (status=final)
            end
        end
    end

    Note over llm,tts: 以下為後續擴充流程 (尚未完整串接)
    llm->>s: text stream (planned)
    s->>tts: text to speech request (planned)
    tts-->>u: audio stream (planned)
